{"lastModified":1775228051474,"uri":"c::7819307041::vessel::d5cca390-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nDiscover our premium yacht fleet: sailing catamarans Lagoon 52F and Lagoon 50. Oneida yachts feature impressive layouts providing VIP double cabins all with private facilities and fully air-conditioned. Our yachts are fully equipped with exclusive furniture and amenities for an unforgettable and relaxing stay on board. \n\nThe ultimate location for your dreamy holidays in the charming Greek landscape. The Oneida Experience suits everyone: families, couples and groups of friends. Each catamaran is spacious and bright, with deluxe cabins and elegant living areas. Enjoy a five-star treatment while sailing from island to island, far from the crowds, exploring hidden bays and beaches. \n","blueprint":{"name":"ONEIDA 2","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca390-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100317-Yla1wM7Gz.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca390-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3442a560-1aae-11f0-9592-3f5d0dbf1c14/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca390-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::34824670-1aae-11f0-9592-3f5d0dbf1c14/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca390-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::346d10c0-1aae-11f0-9592-3f5d0dbf1c14/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca390-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::348309c0-1aae-11f0-9592-3f5d0dbf1c14/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca390-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::34582930-1aae-11f0-9592-3f5d0dbf1c14/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca390-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::346b6310-1aae-11f0-9592-3f5d0dbf1c14/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca390-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::348071b0-1aae-11f0-9592-3f5d0dbf1c14/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca390-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3481d140-1aae-11f0-9592-3f5d0dbf1c14/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca390-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::347fd570-1aae-11f0-9592-3f5d0dbf1c14/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca390-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::34585040-1aae-11f0-9592-3f5d0dbf1c14/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca390-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3442cc70-1aae-11f0-9592-3f5d0dbf1c14/{imageVariant}"],"make":"Lagoon","model":"Lagoon 50","maxCrew":3,"sleeps":8,"basePort":{"uri":"a::place::103e6b1e-b3ee-11ed-af00-325096b39f47","name":"Preveza","coordinates":{"latitude":38.95968634,"longitude":20.75395121},"country":"Greece"},"builtYear":2022,"architect":"","interiorDesigner":"","refitYear":"","topSpeed":"","cruiseSpeed":8,"fuelCapacity":0,"cabinLayout":[{"label":"Double Cabins","value":"4"}],"cabins":4,"bathrooms":4,"length":15.24,"beam":8.14,"draft":1.43,"hullType":"Catamaran","hullConstruction":"","tonnage":"","superStructure":[],"engines":"2 x 80hp Yanmar","amenities":[{"label":"Air Conditioning"},{"label":"Deck Shower"},{"label":"Bimini"},{"label":"Generator"},{"label":"Ice Maker"},{"label":"Inverter"},{"label":"Hairdryers"},{"label":"Water Maker"}],"toys":[{"label":"Water Skis Kids"},{"label":"Snorkel Gear"},{"label":"Tube"},{"label":"Swim Platform"},{"label":"SU Paddle Boards","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Sea Scooters","quantity":"2"}],"entertainment":["Salon Tv","Salon Stereo","Onboard WIFI"],"tenders":["Highfield 340 25hp outboard"]},"crew":[{"name":"Dimitris Bokolas","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca390-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c38a98f0-1aad-11f0-a900-ad595b00eed9/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"“Sea is my life” is Dimitris’s life quote. Since he was a child he remembers himself in a boat. He is an experienced sailor and captain of power and sailing boats. The first boat he was captain in, was his family’s 55ft. traditional Greek Kaiki. Since then he had the opportunity to sail around Greek waters with different kind of boats. During all these years he came across of all kind of weather and sea conditions which made him familiar with\nthe difficult Greek seas. His natural capability of communicate with people and the fact that he can remain calm in any unpredictable situation, creates for his passengers and fellow crew members a feeling of comfort, relaxation and above all safeness during the travel."},{"name":"Zoe Chatzeathanasiou","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca390-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c78fa670-1aad-11f0-a900-ad595b00eed9/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"My name is Zoe. I am a professional chef with 7 years of experience. During these years I have worked in different kind of restaurants, gaining skills and experience next to award winning Greek chefs. Although my culinary expertise is mainly based on Mediterranean cuisine, I really like experimenting with different tastes and variety of cuisines as well. I am passionate not only about cooking but also about nature, so my free time I enjoy exploring and hiking."},{"name":"Petros Filos","role":"Captain","bio":"Petros was born in 2002 in Athens and holds a speed boat license and a sailing license. Over the past season, he has gained significant experience, strong skills in dinghy operation, crew management, first aid, and basic mechanical and electrical knowledge. Known for his communication skills and team spirit he is dedicated to ensuring the safety and satisfaction of both crew and guests. His dedication and expertise to the team, makes him a valuable asset. Beyond sailing, he has a strong passion for sports. He speaks Greek and English."}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":1500000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":1500000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":1950000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":1950000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"Low Season","effectiveD